## ğŸ” **Post-Installation Tips**

* Access UI: `http://<your-server-ip>/nagios`
* Login: `nagiosadmin` + password you set
* Plugin commands live in: `/usr/local/nagios/libexec`
* Config files in: `/usr/local/nagios/etc`

